# Shared image pool — co-deck variant
#
# Image-curator writes shared-pool images here as `presentations/assets/images/<slug>.<ext>`.
# html-build references them from per-project decks via `../assets/images/<slug>.<ext>`.
# This empty folder is scaffolded into every new co-deck project so the shared pool exists at
# new-project time. Kept under version control via this .gitkeep.
